&lt;p&gt;सामान्य गति &lt;br&gt;
&lt;audio controls&gt;
&lt;source src=&#34;https://raw.githubusercontent.com/dasarpai/DAI-mp3/main/dasarpai-mp3/005-ShivTandavaStotram.mp3&#34; type=&#34;audio/mp3&#34;&gt;
